OL,3,CCar found abandoned in Babbs Mill Lake
OL,5,FEmergency services have been called to
OL,6,FBabbs Mill Lake, in Solihull, after a
OL,7,Fcar was found abandoned in the water.
OL,9,FWest Midlands Fire Service said they
OL,10,Fwere called out just after 12pm on
OL,11,FTuesday, March 17.
OL,13,FThe service confirmed a vehicle was
OL,14,Ffound and that checks were carried out
OL,15,Fin the surrounding area, but no one
OL,16,Fwas found inside the vehicle or nearby.
OL,18,FThey now say that their enquiries are
OL,19,Fongoing.
