OL,3,CCar found abandoned in Babbs Mill Lake
OL,5,FA statement from the service reads:
OL,6,F"We were called to Babbs Mill Lake
OL,7,Fjust after 12.05pm this afternoon to
OL,8,Freports a vehicle was found abandoned
OL,9,Fin the water.
OL,11,F"Our colleagues from the fire service
OL,12,Falso attended.
OL,14,F"Following checks of the vehicle and
OL,15,Fsurrounding area no one was found.
OL,16,FEnquiries are ongoing to identify the
OL,17,Fregistered keeper."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/3
